document.full_text: libyan government forces destroyed four fuel storage tanks and set several others ablaze in rebel-held misrata, dealing a blow to the port city's ability to withstand a government siege, rebels said on saturday.
document.title: libyan forces destroy misrata fuel tanks: rebels
